											<h6 class="font-weight-bold">SENDER:</h6>
											<ol>
											<li><span class="font-weight-bold">How do I send packages using Vedagram?</span>
											<br>
											<p>Open the APP, select the Pickup Location and Delivery Location in the App. Also provide the information of the ITEM to be sent and the weight. The App will provide the rates applicable and also a time for pickup</p>
											</li>
											<li> <span class="font-weight-bold">How safe is it to send my package through Vedagram?</span>
											<p>Our delivery agents are well trained and have desired carrying cases for transporting your packages. The packages will be delivered by them carefully to the destined locations without any damage. We also cover your packages with Insurance.</p></li>
										<li><span class="font-weight-bold">What can I send through Vedagram?</span>
										<p>You can send &ndash; Home Cooked Food, Medicines, Clothes, Your electronic gadgets, Wallet, Letters, Gifts, Flower Bouquets, Grocery, Vegetables, Fruits, Books, Mobile, Spare parts for Mobile, Computers, Laptops, etc. We keep expanding to add more items to this list when we deem our deliverers are trained to handle those products.</p></li>
										<li> <span class="font-weight-bold">Will you store the Package I send overnight before delivering?</span>
										<p>No, we do not store your packages overnight, we deliver them the same day.</p></li>
										<li><span class="font-weight-bold">How do I track my Package?</span>
										<p>Vedagram App provides you an exact shipment tracking for your package. It will also provide you the exact time of pickup as well.</p></li>
										</ol>
										<h6 class="font-weight-bold">DELIVERER:</h6>
											<ol>
											<li><span class="font-weight-bold"> How do I register as a Deliverer?</span>
											<br>
											<p>Click the link (Need to provide a link to InfoCareer Recruitment page) and register yourself. You will also be asked for uploading your ID and Address Proof copies for verification. Please keep them handy.  Once uploaded, we will get in touch with you to discuss and onboard.	</p>
											</li>
											<li> <span class="font-weight-bold">How do I get compensated in Vedagram?</span>
											<p>Once you register with us, you will be assigned to Pick and Drop packages across the city. You will be compensated on every delivery you make. You will be provided all the information on the compensation during your onboarding.</p></li>
										<li><span class="font-weight-bold"> What are the prerequisites for registering as a Deliverer?</span>
										<p>You need to have a Two Wheeler, Valid License and Valid Insurance to the vehicle. You will also need to provide your ID and Address proofs. Helmet is a must</p></li>
										<li> <span class="font-weight-bold">What all the covers Vedagram will provide me as Deliverer?</span>
										<p>You get an Accident Cover as part of your association with Vedagram as Deliverer. You also will be covered on the goods you carry to deliver.</p></li>
										</ol>
										<h6 class="font-weight-bold">VENDOR:</h6>
											<ol>
											<li><span class="font-weight-bold"> How do I benefit from partnering with Vedagram?</span>
											<br>
											<p>Vedagram will help you in delivering your goods / packages to your customers on your behalf. It takes away the need to employ a deliverer at your end to manage these deliveries. We also pick packages from your customers. All the packages will be covered by Insurance coverage for transit</p>
											</li>
											<li> <span class="font-weight-bold">How do I get information about my Package delivery?</span>
											<p>Vedagram App will have a live shipment tracking, which will give you the exact details for the delivery. We can also provide you SMS based confirmation after the delivery</p></li>
										<li><span class="font-weight-bold">How do I get Payment from my customers?</span>
										<p>You can use Vedagram Payment gateway for collecting your payment of the product, which in turn we will transfer it to you once the transaction is complete.</p></li>
										<li> <span class="font-weight-bold"> Can you pick packages for me as well?</span>
										<p>Yes, we can pick packages for you as well. It works the same way as you send a package.</p></li>
										<li><span class="font-weight-bold">Why should I partner with Vedagram?</span>
										<p>With Vedagram, your delivery issues are taken care off. We not only deliver close to you, but we can deliver farther from you as well. You can grow your business across the city by delivering through you, it provides a unique opportunity to expand your business faster. We have the city covered with our Deliverers, who will be your last mile connectivity to your customers.</p></li>
										</ol>
										
